snippet.title: [MAME] Game & Watch: Mario's Bombs Away (c)1983 Nintendo
snippet.description: Support for this will be in MAME 0.213, thanks to algestam for the emulation and hydef for the artwork.  Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5
